{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Expenses and benefits: inducement (golden hello) payments"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/expenses-and-benefits-inducement-payments.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/expenses-and-benefits-inducement-payments"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"B846","business_proposition":true,"alternative_title":"Employers' tax and reporting for inducement (golden hello) paymentsa","overview":"Tax and reporting rules for employers providing inducement (golden hello) payments","updated_at":"2012-10-03T17:03:06+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Inducement (often called \u2018golden hello\u2019) payments counts as earnings.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You&rsquo;ll need to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>add the payments to your employee\u2019s other earnings</li>\n  <li>deduct and pay <abbr title=\"Pay As You Earn\">PAYE</abbr> tax and Class 1 National Insurance through payroll</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Technical guidance</h2>\n\n<p>The following guides contain more detailed information:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/manuals/eimanual/eim00700.htm\" title=\"Employment income: inducement payments\">employment income: inducement payments</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/manuals/nimmanual/nim02185.htm\" title=\"Class 1 NICs: 'golden hellos'\">Class 1 <abbr title=\"National Insurance contributions\">NICs</abbr>: &lsquo;golden hellos&rsquo;</a></p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"Expenses and employee benefits","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/business%2Fe